# =============================================================================
# HOMZEN REAL ESTATE DESIGN SYSTEM (Cursor Rules)
# =============================================================================
# Strict 1:1 clone of target Homzen landing page design.
# Apply these rules to ALL component creation and redesigns.

## TYPOGRAPHY HIERARCHY
- HEADINGS (H1, H2, H3, section titles, hero headline): 
  Font: 'Poppins' (sans-serif, NO SERIFS, font-sans)
  Weights: font-bold (700) or font-semibold (600)
  Color: text-[#1A1A2E] (dark navy)
  Letter-spacing: -0.5px
  Line-height: 1.15 to 1.2 (tight, clean)
  
- BODY TEXT (descriptions, property features, paragraph text):
  Font: 'Poppins' (sans-serif)
  Weights: font-regular (400) or font-medium (500)
  Color: text-[#555555] (medium gray)
  Line-height: 1.6 to 1.65 (breathing room)

- UI TEXT (buttons, labels, tags, filters, prices, counts):
  Font: 'Poppins' (sans-serif)
  Weights: font-medium (500) or font-semibold (600)
  Color: Varies by context (see COLOR PALETTE below)
  Font-size: 12px to 16px (crisp, precise)

- SMALL TEXT (metadata, captions, helper text):
  Font: 'Poppins' (sans-serif)
  Weight: font-regular (400)
  Color: text-[#717171] (muted gray)
  Size: 11px to 13px

## COLOR PALETTE (Tailwind Config)
Primary Background:
  - bg-[#FFFFFF] (pure white) — section backgrounds
  - bg-[#F8F8F8] (soft gray) — alternate sections

Accent / CTA Color:
  - bg-[#E84040] or text-[#E84040] (coral-red) — ONLY for:
    ✓ Primary action buttons (Find Properties, Submit Property, etc.)
    ✓ Selected/active states (tabs, filters, badges)
    ✓ Highlight text, urgency markers
  - Hover: #CC3232 (darker coral)
  - Do NOT over-use; reserve for primary emphasis only

Text Colors:
  - text-[#1A1A2E] (#1A1A2E) — headings, dark text
  - text-[#555555] (#555555) — primary body text
  - text-[#717171] (#717171) — secondary, labels, metadata
  - text-[#AAAAAA] (#AAAAAA) — disabled, placeholder text, muted

Borders & Dividers:
  - border-[#E5E5E5] (light gray)
  - Use subtle dividers; avoid harsh blacks

Backgrounds (Cards & Sections):
  - bg-[#FFFFFF] for cards on white sections
  - bg-[#F8F8F8] for subtle card backgrounds

## ICONOGRAPHY RULES (CRITICAL)
Property Feature Icons (Beds, Baths, Sq Ft, Garage, Type, Location):
  - STYLE: Bold, heavy-weight, detailed, intricate icons (NOT thin lines)
  - SOURCE: Font Awesome 6 (solid weight), Phosphor Icons (fill weight), or custom SVG
  - Weight: Bold/Solid appearance, fill-based (not stroke-based)
  - Size: 18px to 28px (prominent, not delicate)
  - Color: text-[#555555] or text-[#1A1A2E]
  - AVOID: Lucide React thin icons, stroke-based outlines (creates AI-slop look)

System / Utility Icons (Arrows, Chevrons, Close, Hamburger, Search, Filter):
  - Use Lucide React for these functional utilities ONLY
  - Stroke weight: stroke-[1.5] or stroke-[2]
  - Color: text-[#555555] or text-[#1A1A2E]
  - Size: 16px to 20px

Icon + Text Spacing:
  - gap-2 (8px) for compact UI elements
  - gap-3 (12px) for featured sections

## LAYOUT & WHITESPACE
Section Padding (Vertical):
  - py-20 (80px) for major sections
  - py-16 (64px) for moderate sections
  - py-12 (48px) for smaller sections
  - ALWAYS maintain breathing room

Container Max-Width:
  - max-w-7xl (1280px) for primary content
  - Horizontal padding: px-20 (80px) on desktop, px-10 (40px) on tablet, px-5 (20px) on mobile

Card Styling:
  - bg-[#FFFFFF] with subtle shadow: shadow-sm (0 8px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.10))
  - Border-radius: rounded-xl (12px) or rounded-2xl (16px)
  - Padding: p-6 (24px) for standard cards
  - Border: Optional border-[#E5E5E5] (1px) for definition

Grid Layout (Property Cards, Feature Grid):
  - Desktop (1024px+): grid-cols-4 for standard cards
  - Tablet (768px+): grid-cols-2
  - Mobile (< 768px): grid-cols-1
  - Gap: gap-6 (24px) between cards

Hover States:
  - Subtle lift: hover:shadow-lg
  - Smooth transition: transition-all duration-300
  - Text color shift: hover:text-[#E84040]
  - Keep refined, no aggressive transforms

## BUTTON STANDARDS
Primary Button (CTA):
  - bg-[#E84040], text-white
  - px-6 py-3 (24px × 12px)
  - font-poppins font-semibold text-sm
  - rounded-lg, shadow-sm
  - hover:bg-[#CC3232], transition-colors duration-200

Secondary Button:
  - bg-[#F8F8F8], text-[#1A1A2E]
  - px-6 py-3
  - font-poppins font-medium text-sm
  - rounded-lg
  - hover:bg-[#E5E5E5]

Outline Button:
  - border-1.5 border-[#E5E5E5], bg-transparent, text-[#333333]
  - px-6 py-3
  - font-poppins font-medium text-sm
  - rounded-lg
  - hover:border-[#E84040], hover:text-[#E84040]

## RESPONSIVE DESIGN
- Mobile-First: Design for 375px, scale up
- Breakpoints: sm (640px), md (768px), lg (1024px), xl (1280px)
- Hero Section: Single column on mobile, side-by-side on desktop
- Property Grid: Adjust columns per breakpoint
- Typography: Reduce heading size on mobile (text-4xl → text-2xl)
- Padding: Reduce px on mobile; increase on desktop

## COMPONENT ARCHITECTURE
- Use Tailwind Utility Classes exclusively
- Leverage component reusability (Card, Button, Badge, IconLabel)
- Map all colors to hex values (no arbitrary colors)
- Use Next.js Image component for all property photos
- Implement lazy-loading for below-fold images

## STRICT DO's AND DON'Ts
DO:
  ✓ Use 'Poppins' for ALL text (serif-free)
  ✓ Use bold/solid icons for property features (Font Awesome/Phosphor solid)
  ✓ Apply bg-[#FFFFFF] and bg-[#F8F8F8] for sections
  ✓ Use text-[#E84040] ONLY for primary CTAs and highlights
  ✓ Maintain generous section padding (py-20/py-16)
  ✓ Soft shadows (shadow-sm) and rounded corners
  ✓ Test hover states on all interactive elements
  ✓ Keep icons bold, detailed, heavy-weight

DON'T:
  ✗ Use serif fonts (no Cormorant Garamond, no Georgia)
  ✗ Use pure black (#000000); use text-[#1A1A2E]
  ✗ Over-use text-[#E84040]; reserve for primary emphasis
  ✗ Use thin-stroke icons on property cards (Lucide only for utilities)
  ✗ Create cramped layouts; prioritize breathing room
  ✗ Use harsh shadows or aggressive transforms
  ✗ Mix serif and sans-serif on same component
  ✗ Use arbitrary Tailwind colors; stick to defined palette

## DESIGN REFERENCES
- Target Image: Homzen Landing Page (1:1 clone)
- Primary Font: Poppins (NO serifs, all weights 400-700)
- Icon Style: Bold, solid, detailed, intricate (heavy-weight appearance)
- Primary Color: #E84040 (coral-red for CTAs only)
- Background: #FFFFFF and #F8F8F8
- Dark Text: #1A1A2E, Body: #555555, Muted: #717171